[Predict the seven people's
love lines based on clues!]

2017
01:38:05,296 --> 01:38:07,166
Which ones are easy?

2018
01:38:07,166 --> 01:38:09,136
- Min Ju. Min Ju.
- Min Ju, Seong Min?

2019
01:38:09,136 --> 01:38:12,716
- At least for today.
- Min Ju is the easiest.

2020
01:38:12,716 --> 01:38:15,896
Min Ju, Seong Min.

2021
01:38:15,896 --> 01:38:17,356
Yu Gyeong is easy, too.

2022
01:38:17,356 --> 01:38:18,826
Wu Yeol.

2023
01:38:18,826 --> 01:38:20,256
Yu Gyeong, Wu Yeol.

2024
01:38:20,256 --> 01:38:22,366
She gave him her artery.

2025
01:38:22,366 --> 01:38:24,766
[Predicting Yu Gyeong chooses Wu Yeol]

2026
01:38:24,766 --> 01:38:27,786
I think Seo Won gave up on Yu Gyeong.

2027
01:38:27,786 --> 01:38:31,456
He was in shock because of Yu Gyeong.

2028
01:38:31,456 --> 01:38:32,736
Who will he choose, then?

2029
01:38:32,736 --> 01:38:36,816
Min Ju and Seo Won were together today.

2030
01:38:36,816 --> 01:38:38,806
They cooked together.

2031
01:38:38,806 --> 01:38:40,626
But I didn't notice any chemistry.

2032
01:38:40,626 --> 01:38:43,856
Right. They were just like friends.

2033
01:38:43,856 --> 01:38:45,606
I think Kim Seo Won chooses Jeong Gyu Ri.

2034
01:38:45,606 --> 01:38:47,396
- Jeong Gyu Ri.
- Me, too. Me, too.

2035
01:38:47,396 --> 01:38:49,806
Gyu Ri's occupation was unexpected.

2036
01:38:49,806 --> 01:38:51,566
She's older than him, too.

2037
01:38:51,566 --> 01:38:53,256
- I think it's Gyu Ri.
- It's Gyu Ri.

2038
01:38:53,256 --> 01:38:55,936
He must've started noticing Noona.

2039
01:38:55,936 --> 01:38:57,746
And now, Seong Min.

2040
01:38:57,746 --> 01:39:00,036
Seong Min chose Yu Gyeong yesterday.

2041
01:39:00,036 --> 01:39:04,476
And he wasn't shocked
by her age reveal, either.

2042
01:39:04,476 --> 01:39:06,086
That didn't matter.

2043
01:39:06,086 --> 01:39:07,926
He has no reason to change his mind.

2044
01:39:07,926 --> 01:39:09,616
He might've moved on to Min Ju.

2045
01:39:09,616 --> 01:39:13,906
When her face turned red,
he kept giving her water.

2046
01:39:13,906 --> 01:39:17,596
As a dermatologist, he recommends
water when your face turns red.

2047
01:39:17,596 --> 01:39:18,796
You think that was it?

2048
01:39:18,796 --> 01:39:21,246
They were walking together to the bar, too.

2049
01:39:21,246 --> 01:39:24,206
And Min Ju prepared him a meal.

2050
01:39:24,206 --> 01:39:26,186
Min Ju prepared him a meal, too.

2051
01:39:26,186 --> 01:39:29,266
She made him fried eggs. I forgot about that.

2052
01:39:29,266 --> 01:39:33,946
Hold on. Roy is insisting on this now.

2053
01:39:33,946 --> 01:39:35,996
- Last week...
- I'm suddenly nervous.

2054
01:39:35,996 --> 01:39:39,366
- I think it's Min Ju.
- I'm nervous that he's so sure.

2055
01:39:39,366 --> 01:39:42,026
Seong Min might've felt Min Ju's interest.

2056
01:39:42,026 --> 01:39:44,896
The only problem is that Roy is pushing this.

2057
01:39:44,896 --> 01:39:47,326
- Okay.
- I'm nervous, but...

2058
01:39:47,326 --> 01:39:50,296
[Choosing Min Ju for Seong Min]

2059
01:39:50,296 --> 01:39:52,066
How about Jun Hyeon?

2060
01:39:52,066 --> 01:39:53,556
I think it's Yu Gyeong.

2061
01:39:53,556 --> 01:39:54,756
I'm sure of it.

2062
01:39:54,756 --> 01:39:59,096
I saw him staring a lot
while they were flirting.

2063
01:39:59,096 --> 01:40:01,516
- Roy Kim, you think it's Yu Gyeong?
- Yes.

2064
01:40:01,516 --> 01:40:03,226
Let's go with Gyu Ri.

2065
01:40:03,226 --> 01:40:05,156
That's enough of dismissing Roy.

2066
01:40:05,156 --> 01:40:07,326
[Dismissed]

2067
01:40:07,326 --> 01:40:08,616
Dismiss?

2068
01:40:08,616 --> 01:40:10,286
- It's Gyu Ri.
- Is it?

2069
01:40:10,286 --> 01:40:13,226
They talked about Italy and Spain.

2070
01:40:13,226 --> 01:40:16,266
Kim Eana has the best radar.

2071
01:40:16,266 --> 01:40:18,096
But I think it's Yu Gyeong.

2072
01:40:18,096 --> 01:40:21,236
- That's more reason.
- Okay.

2073
01:40:21,236 --> 01:40:24,026
We only have Gyu Ri and Wu Yeol left.

2074
01:40:24,026 --> 01:40:25,306
Gyu Ri and Wu Yeol.

2075
01:40:25,306 --> 01:40:27,396
I think Gyu Ri chooses Wu Yeol.

2076
